MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

MAJOR CHANGES:
- Migrated Google and Facebook OAuth from Sharetribe SDK to Supabase
- Created new Supabase OAuth handlers to replace legacy Sharetribe flow
- Updated all OAuth callbacks to use Supabase authentication
- Email/password auth already working with Supabase (from previous work)

NEW FILES:
- server/api/auth/loginWithSupabaseOAuth.js - OAuth callback handler (replaces loginWithIdp.js)
- server/api/auth/confirmOAuthSignup.js - OAuth confirmation endpoint (replaces createUserWithIdp.js)

UPDATED FILES:
Backend:
- server/auth/supabase-auth.js - Added signInWithOAuth() and getOrCreateUserFromOAuth()
- server/api/auth/google.js - Updated to use Supabase OAuth instead of Sharetribe SDK
- server/api/auth/facebook.js - Updated to use Supabase OAuth instead of Sharetribe SDK
- server/apiRouter.js - Added route for /auth/confirm-oauth-signup, updated comments

Frontend:
- src/ducks/auth.duck.js - Updated signupWithIdpThunk to handle Supabase session tokens
- src/util/api.js - Updated createUserWithIdp() to call new Supabase endpoint

AUTHENTICATION STATUS:
✅ Email/Password Login - Working (Supabase)
✅ Email/Password Signup - Working (Supabase)
✅ Google OAuth - Migrated to Supabase
✅ Facebook OAuth - Migrated to Supabase
✅ Session Management - Working (Supabase tokens)
✅ Token Refresh - Working (Supabase)
✅ Current User Fetching - Working (Supabase)

NEXT STEPS:
- Test OAuth flows in development
- Remove old Sharetribe files (loginWithIdp.js, createUserWithIdp.js)
- Continue with Phase 2 (Listings migration)
